data.description: Fabulous Foothills desert beauty! Offering a spacious 4bd, 2ba, open floor plan. Vaulted ceilings & tile flooring flow delightfully throughout the living areas. Perfect for entertaining, the newly installed glass slider opens up to the large patio and refreshing pool! Freshly poured concrete in the RV port. Paid-in-full solar panels are a PLUS! Home exterior recently painted & new front door just installed. Located just blocks away from MDS golf course, shopping, restaurants, & the Fortuna Foothills desert!
